description: Southern Duo Shane & Shayla are wowing foodies on the streets of Atlanta with Cattywampus Grill, where they’re shakin’ up good ‘ole American eats with the best bold flavors found in the south. Only the finest and freshest locally sourced ingredients are used to make Cattywampus’ cuisine, which includes their famous Cluckin’ Waffle- juicy shredded fried chicken topped with creamy white cheddar cheese, crisp dill pickles, and chive mayo syrup, all smothered between a fresh-made waffle. If you think this sounds incredible enough, just wait till you see that the waffle is pink!You will also find incredible sides, like fresh hot French Fries, cheesy creamy Grit Fritters, and three cheese Mac ‘n’ Cheese, mmmm, it simply just doesn’t get any better. For all this and more, come visit Cattywampus Grill for your next satisfying fill of delicious Southern dishes.
name: Cattywampus Grill
